'''Kurtz''' is a [[franco]] living on the [[Village of the Francos]], in [[Mr. Kurtz's house|a house]] where he made sure no sunlight can come in. His flowers are the proof of that.

According to the sign outside his house, Mr. Kurtz is a retired colonel. He currently works as a scientist. Like most of the francos, Mr. Kurtz is also in a treasure hunt after the lost [[Francos fragment|fragment]].

Mr. Kurtz has no vital role in the game. He tells [[Twinsen]] that he concoted a potion which should allow him to determine the location of the lost fragment, but he lost the vial.

